        <h3 class="tzTitle">
            本版热门</h3>
        <ul class="pp">
            <li><a onclick="GaqPush('本版热门-焦点图')" target='_blank' title='中越战争中方战俘首度直面镜头:没死很愧疚' href='http://bbs.tiexue.net/post_9700121_1.html'><img id='img1' src='http://small2.itiexue.net/2089/20892986.jpg' width='120' height='90' border=0></a><span><a onclick="GaqPush('本版热门-焦点图')" target='_blank' title='中越战争中方战俘首度直面镜头:没死很愧疚' href='http://bbs.tiexue.net/post_9700121_1.html'>中越战争中方战俘首度直面镜头:没死很愧疚</a></span></li>
